由之前開始一直都冇改變<br />\n當然啦咁樣犧牲完有冇意義呢啲就唔係討論範圍，見到個個都話Floch變condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有佢講Mikasa嗰段都好突兀<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/sigh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實我覺得爛尾嘅唔係最後結局如何、每個角色下場係點，而係佢最後嘅對話可唔可以解釋得返晒所有嘅動機去說服讀者，去畀讀者理解之前嗰個性格180度改變嘅Eren<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tired.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"618a2b48a7fc51a05a7f5fd2867df0595199f11f","tid":2479422,"uid":180124,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b94ab3f597e9f6e7f1ab3075be41c4e128cab005","tid":2479422,"uid":253320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d4f050636e711f9c77aaec6684c748b79cbcc5e","tid":2479422,"uid":196184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"223a933980671c32b3d6799fbfa97f99bc5b112d","tid":2479422,"uid":196184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T21:03:19.000Z","msg":"爛尾就爛尾啦<br />\n始尾精蟲都無交代點處理<br />\n創狗射後不理<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T21:04:03.000Z","msg":"始<span class=\"red\">祖</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T21:08:54.000Z","msg":"1. 條蟲係砍頭之後消失左。個結局有交代，係冇一格有show到蟲蟲消失咁解。咁依一格係唔係要畫埋可以斟酌。<br />\n2. 巨人之力消失先係結局重點。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T21:10:59.000Z","msg":"我諗令連登仔最難接受係佢地屌左幾個月最唔想出現既左膠和解結局真係出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed749e5992e877f45bc8f9a3b86e92f105928ebd","tid":2479422,"uid":196184,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"176dece220e62c57fb94a57334564e07091c650f","tid":2479422,"uid":187368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0d1aa27b518075a7300eb6cbfc5a1fd02c85a75","tid":2479422,"uid":196184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"199ed92365b3e8543b244549874d90b188a6b971","tid":2479422,"uid":187368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T20:55:17.000Z","msg":"我意思係唔明仲未滅蟲個陣<br />\n女皇點解要懷孕<br />\n冇記錯之前睇分析<br />\n好似話想避免女皇唔會冇la